definitions.definition: A member of a confederacy of (originally) five Native American (Indian) tribes : the Mohawks , the Oneidas , the Onondagas , the Cayugas , and the Senecas . Also known as the Iroquois League.
A kind of hairdo where both sides of the head are shaved, leaving only a stripe of hair in the middle.

definitions.definition: Any of the languages of the Iroquois, belonging to the Iroquoian family of languages.
